Class Booking

java.lang.Object
Booking
Direct Known Subclasses:
Reservation, WalkIn
public abstract class Booking extends Object
A booking for a table in a restaurant. A booking contains a date, start time, number of people and restaurant ID, all of which are decided by the user. The booking also contains some internal data like bookingID which will be handled by the Restaurant class and the end time which by default is the start time + 2 hours.
